{
  "texts": [
    "The BN layer performs standardization and normalization on the input from the previous layer, scaling the input values.",
    "Additionally, higher-resolution inputs are utilized.",
    "All of these improvements enhance accuracy.In the new structure of predicting boundaries, YOLO V3 adds logistic regression to predict the score of each bounding box.",
    "The Faster R-CNN method was also introduced, and only one bounding box was given priority.",
    "These small improvements lead to big improvements."
  ]
}